title: Bioacoustics Model Zoo
description: collection of pretrained models for bioacoustic classification tasks
soundProcessingFeatures: use MixIT Bird sound source separation model to separate audio into channels potentially representing separate sources
acousticParameterMeasurement: create embeddings for audio data using 3 common bioacoustic classifiers (Perch, BirdNET, HawkEars)
classifierFeatures: run 3 common bird sound classifiers (Perch, BirdNET, HawkEars)
